The Anatomy of a Format Specifier:

Syntax :

       %[flags][width][.precision][length]type
       flags: - (left align) ,+(show plus sign),0(pad with zeros)

       width: Eg:%4d

       .precision: Eg:%.4f

       length: l for long or h for short
